@page
@model IndexModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home";
    ViewData["Description"] = "ePegboard runs your badminton club night - fair, balanced games with smart picking, attendance reports and member stats. Free for at least 60 days at play.epegboard.com.";
}
    <div class="text-center" style="padding-top: 30px;">
        <div id="heroCarousel" class="carousel slide carousel-fade carousel-dark mx-auto" data-bs-ride="carousel" data-bs-interval="4500" style="max-width: 720px;">
            <div class="carousel-indicators">
                <button type="button" data-bs-target="#heroCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Mid-session dashboard"></button>
                <button type="button" data-bs-target="#heroCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Live attendee stats"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-inner rounded shadow-sm">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="~/Images/site-dashboard.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="ePegboard mid-session dashboard - 4 courts running" />
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/Images/site-attendee-stats.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Live attendee stats - per-player ratings, win percentage, and match history during the session" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="padding: 30px 15px;">
            <h2 style="color: darkgreen; font-weight: bold;">Smarter Club Nights. Fairer Games.</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
                ePegboard runs your club night - smart picking, attendance tracking, live stats, and the fairness your players keep asking for. Runs in any browser on any device, with no install.
            </p>
            <a class="btn btn-success btn-lg mt-3" href="https://play.epegboard.com/signup" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Try Free at play.epegboard.com</a>

            <p style="margin-top: 12px; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555;">
                Free for at least 60 days. No card details. Tablet or laptop-sized screens recommended for the best experience.
            </p>

            <p style="margin-top: 20px; color: #333; font-weight: 500;">
                Already powering club nights throughout Milton Keynes - and expanding across the UK and Ireland.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section style="padding: 30px 20px; background-color: #ffffff; border-top: 1px solid #eee; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">
        <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <h4 class="text-center" style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 18px;">Two ways to use ePegboard</h4>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                    <div class="p-3 rounded h-100" style="background-color: #f1f8f3; border: 1px solid #cfe9d6;">
                        <h5 style="color: darkgreen; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px;">🌐 Web app <span class="badge bg-success ms-1" style="font-weight: 500;">Recommended</span></h5>
                        <p class="mb-2" style="font-size: 0.95rem;">
                            Runs in any browser on any device. No install. Free for at least 60 days, no card details. New features land here first.
                        </p>
                        <a href="https://play.epegboard.com/signup" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-success btn-sm">Try free at play.epegboard.com</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="p-3 rounded h-100" style="background-color: #f6f7f9; border: 1px solid #d6dae0;">
                        <h5 style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px;">💻 Desktop app (Windows)</h5>
                        <p class="mb-2" style="font-size: 0.95rem;">
                            Fully offline - the right choice if your venue has unreliable internet. £60/year per club after a 60-day free trial.
                        </p>
                        <a asp-page="/FeaturesDesktop" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm">See desktop features</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="text-center" style="padding: 40px 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa;">
        <div class="container" style="max-width: 850px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <h3 style="font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">Your Club Night, Perfectly Run</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 15px;">
                ePegboard auto-generates balanced games using player ratings, waiting times, and rotation history - while giving the operator full control when needed. Whoever's running the session just opens the app in their browser and goes.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
                From smart picking and pick explanations to fairness statistics, ratings graphs, and built-in attendance reports, ePegboard handles the details so you can focus on great sessions. Real clubs use it now; new features ship most weeks.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding: 60px 20px; background-color: #ffffff;">
        <div class="container text-center" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <a href="~/Images/pegboard-vs-epegboard2.png" target="_blank">
            <img src="~/Images/pegboard-vs-epegboard2.png"
                 alt="Traditional pegboard vs. ePegboard software"
                 class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" />
            </a>

            <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: #555; margin-top: 15px;">
                From manual pegboards to intelligent court assignment - all in your browser, no install needed.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding: 60px 20px; background-color: #ffffff;">
        <div class="container" style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <h3 class="text-center" style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 40px;">How Club Nights Work with ePegboard</h3>

            <!-- Step 1 -->
            <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img src="~/Images/add_player_photos.jpg" alt="Player sign-in screen" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h5>1. Add Players</h5>
                    <p>Register players as they arrive - including drop-ins and last-minute changes. Just start typing their name or click from the photo gallery. Photos help newcomers identify partners quickly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2 -->
            <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
                    <img src="~/Images/Next_game_sample.jpg" alt="Court assignment screen" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                    <h5>2. Let ePegboard Build the Games</h5>
                    <p>Smart auto-pairing based on rest time, past matchups, and player level - or let the first-in-line picker choose with assistive suggestions from the system. Pick explanations show players exactly why each game was picked.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 3 -->
            <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img src="~/Images/full_court.jpg" alt="Game announcement screen" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h5>3. Announce and Play</h5>
                    <p>Display game assignments clearly on-screen - or announce them via audio if you choose. Everyone knows where to go, and court time stays fully used.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 4 -->
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
                    <a href="~/Images/site-attendee-stats.png" target="_blank">
                        <img src="~/Images/site-attendee-stats.png" alt="Live attendee stats screenshot" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" />
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                    <h5>4. See Your Stats in Real Time</h5>
                    <p>Players track win percentage, rating changes, and full match history during the session. Fairness statistics are visible mid-session, and the leaderboard keeps everyone engaged - especially in competitive clubs.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding: 60px 20px; background-color: #ffffff;">
        <div class="container" style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <h3 class="text-center" style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;">Designed for Everyone on Court</h3>
            <p class="text-center" style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 40px;">
                Don't just assign courts - run the kind of sessions players come back for.
            </p>

            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-md-5 mb-4">
                    <h5>🎾 For Players</h5>
                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0;">
                        <li>✅ Less waiting</li>
                        <li>✅ More balanced games</li>
                        <li>✅ Smarter rotation</li>
                        <li>✅ Live stats and ratings</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-5 mb-4">
                    <h5>📋 For Club Night Organisers</h5>
                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0;">
                        <li>✅ Happy players</li>
                        <li>✅ More renewals and new members</li>
                        <li>✅ Fairer sessions, less effort</li>
                        <li>✅ Attendance reports for retention</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding: 60px 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa;">
        <div class="container" style="max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <h3 class="text-center" style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 40px;">Powerful Features That Make Club Nights Run Smoothly</h3>

            <div class="row text-center">
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5>🎯 Smart Game Picking</h5>
                    <p>Auto-pairing based on ratings, wait time, and fairness - tuned to address the most common complaint we heard: stronger players paired with weak partners.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5>🔍 Pick Explanations</h5>
                    <p>Players see exactly why each game was picked - no more "the algorithm got it wrong" arguments without evidence.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5>📊 Player Stats and Ratings Graphs</h5>
                    <p>Track performance over time, see ratings graphs, and use historic data for league pairings and club decisions.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5>📋 Flexible Game Control</h5>
                    <p>Admins can manually override matchups when needed - balancing tradition with smart automation.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5>🔊 Automated Announcements</h5>
                    <p>Connect to a speaker system and use your device's audio to announce upcoming games and players - no more shouting across the courts.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <h5>📁 Attendance Reports and Exports</h5>
                    <p>Built-in attendance reports for member retention. Export attendance, match history, and payments in common formats.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="text-center py-5 bg-success text-white">
        <h2>Try ePegboard Free for at least 60 days</h2>
        <p class="lead mb-3">No subscription. No card details. Just smarter club nights.</p>
        <a href="https://play.epegboard.com/signup" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-light btn-lg">Sign Up at play.epegboard.com</a>
        <p class="mt-3 mb-0" style="font-size: 0.95rem; opacity: 0.9;">Tablet or laptop-sized screens recommended for the best experience.</p>
    </section>
